name: Serenity
description:
Inspired by the outcome of the current pandemic situation, this artwork focuses on calmness and serenity. In the midst of chaos and confusion faced by many through these tough times, the artwork offers an escape of somesort. Providing a calm and meditative experience for the viewer. Reminding them to take a step back and just breathe. Allowing each thought to pass through without any judgement, and be in the present.
